headline.print_headline: JetBlue Pilots Vote for First Time to Unionize
headline.main: JetBlue Pilots Vote for First Time to Unionize

lead_paragraph: The National Mediation Board said Tuesday that pilots at JetBlue Airways Corp. voted overwhelmingly to unionize, reversing two earlier votes.
